data.description: *OPEN HOUSE 3/20 12-4PM* WELCOME HOME! This gorgeous 4 bedroom home is located in highly desirable Redstone Commons- convenient to all the amenities of town and a short commute to area bases. Put this one on your list to view- floor plan features 4 bedrooms and 3 1/2 baths- FULL, true mother-in-law/guest suite. Suite not only has a full bathroom attached, but separate living quarters as well. This home was built in 2019 and is TURN-KEY! Notable additions have been made, to include WiFI capable sprinkler system, fully fenced backyard, and security system. Kitchen features open and functional layout to living area (see attached floor plan) with granite countertops and stainless steel appliances. There is a formal dining area as well as eat-in breakfast area. THREE-CAR front-entry garage. Move-in ready with covered back porch and all desired upgrade in place. Redstone Commons is a community with a resort style pool and clubhouse, available for owner use and reservation. Schedule your showing today!
